features = [
    'delta_sessions',
    'active_time',
    'session_time',
    'activity'
]
for game in GAMES:
    
    dat = df[df['context'] == game]
    
    for i in range(1, 21):

        fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 4, figsize=(15, 3))
        for ind, ax in enumerate(axs.flatten()):

            temporal_slice = dat[dat['session_order'] == i]
            temporal_slice = temporal_slice[features].values
            sns.distplot(temporal_slice[:, ind], ax=ax, kde=False)

        plt.tight_layout()
        plt.show()

fig, axs = plt.subplots(5, 4, figsize=(20, 25), sharex=True, sharey=True)
axs = axs.flatten()
for session in df['session_order'].unique():
    
    sliced = df[df['session_order'] == session]
    corr = sliced[
        [
            'session_order', 
            'delta_sessions', 
            'active_time', 
            'session_time', 
            'activity'
        ]
    ].corr(method='spearman').values
    
    sns.heatmap(
        corr,
        vmin=-1,
        vmax=1,
        cmap='coolwarm',
        annot=True,
        ax=axs[session-1],
        cbar=False
    )
    
    axs.set_title(f'Session {session-1}')
